'''Sanjiban Ghosh''' (born  6 July 1991 in [[Kolkata]]) is an [[India]]n [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]] for [[Mumbai F.C.|Mumbai]] in the [[I-League]].

==Career==

===Mumbai===
Ghosh started his footballing career with [[Southern Samity]] in Kolkata before joining [[Mumbai F.C.]] of the [[I-League]] in 2011.<ref>{{cite news|author=Mumbai FC |url=http://www.mumbaifc.com/MumbaiFC2012/PlayerInfo.aspx?PlaID=12&CatId=1 |title= SANJIBAN GHOSH |publisher=Mumbai FC |date= |accessdate=2011-02-24}}</ref> He then made his debut for Mumbai in the [[I-League]] on 10 November 2012 against [[Salgaocar S.C.|Salgaocar]], the match finished with Mumbai losing 1-0.<ref>http://www.goal.com/en-india/match/69230/salgaocar-sc-vs-mumbai-fc/report</ref>

